02:22.846 --> 02:25.138
That thing?
Yeah.

02:30.680 --> 02:32.347
Shit.

02:32.347 --> 02:33.514
Dude...

02:39.055 --> 02:40.472
( chuckles )

02:40.472 --> 02:43.930
My God, what the fuck--
