- You're acting weird.

02:47.097 --> 02:49.055
- You're acting weird.
- Are you trippin'?

02:49.055 --> 02:50.805
- No.
- Are you?

02:50.805 --> 02:52.888
- Where were you?
- Dude, where do you
think I was?

02:52.888 --> 02:55.596
( chuckles )

02:55.596 --> 02:57.222
- Dude.
- What?

02:57.222 --> 03:01.013
I got 'em.
Happy birthday,
best friend-o!

03:01.013 --> 03:02.555
Come on, man.
Get 'em.

03:02.555 --> 03:03.888
Fucking get 'em.

03:05.555 --> 03:07.055
( grunts )

03:12.264 --> 03:14.555
Dude, it's fucking
Sound Garden, Melvins,

03:14.555 --> 03:16.888
- Screaming Trees, fucking
Rage Against the Machine!
- No way!

03:16.888 --> 03:19.430
- Dude!
- ( laughing )

03:19.430 --> 03:21.222
Three!

03:21.222 --> 03:23.638
I know it's a lot,
but I really think
it's gonna be worth it

03:23.638 --> 03:24.888
'cause it's
a fucking experience.

03:24.888 --> 03:27.888
Let's just do it.
Let's just go.

03:27.888 --> 03:29.846
These are fucking
crazy cheap.

03:29.846 --> 03:31.930
But I think
it's gonna be worth it.

03:31.930 --> 03:35.596
No, but how are
these so cheap?

03:35.596 --> 03:37.472
Dude, they're 20 bucks,
like, apiece.

03:37.472 --> 03:40.264
No, I know, exactly.
I'm-- I'm just saying...

03:41.846 --> 03:44.389
- Ah, shit.
- What?

03:44.389 --> 03:46.180
This concert.

03:46.180 --> 03:48.097
It's gonna be
sweet as fuck.

03:48.097 --> 03:51.138
No, we-- we are--
( sighs )

03:51.138 --> 03:52.763
we already went
to this concert.

03:54.222 --> 03:55.472
What do you mean?

03:59.138 --> 04:00.763
What's going on?

04:00.763 --> 04:02.055
What?

04:02.055 --> 04:04.972
What's going on
with your fucking face?

04:04.972 --> 04:06.763
What are you
talking about?

04:10.555 --> 04:11.555
Don't do that.

04:13.180 --> 04:14.180
Don't do that!

04:14.180 --> 04:16.430
( panting )

04:16.430 --> 04:18.805
( TV playing )

04:23.264 --> 04:28.389
Man on TV:
...the horrific,
the terrifying cat.

04:28.389 --> 04:30.264
( audience laughing )

04:30.264 --> 04:32.805
