a more friendly guardian?

04:32.805 --> 04:34.930
( audience laughing )

04:43.264 --> 04:45.180
( urinating )

04:45.180 --> 04:49.013
( chuckles )
Fucking Rage Against
the Machine.

04:54.514 --> 04:56.138
( keyboard clicks )

04:59.472 --> 05:02.638
( music playing )

05:02.638 --> 05:04.638
( keyboard clicks )

05:10.013 --> 05:11.389
( exhales )

05:17.680 --> 05:19.555
Can you hear me?

05:23.805 --> 05:26.555
Do you wanna
hang out tonight?

05:29.138 --> 05:31.472
And maybe give me
some advice?

05:34.514 --> 05:37.472
I'm just having
a really hard time...

05:38.846 --> 05:41.180
